{"tid":2294080,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人喺 Rentacamera 租過機？","createTime":"2020-11-20T17:33:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-25T11:18:04.000Z","uid":104734,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"373265ab2601d91867b50a625ca87ac7af39b105","tid":2294080,"uid":104734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T17:33:19.000Z","msg":"是咁的，小弟前日幫襯佢哋租咗部相機，交低咗幾千蚊做按金。<br />\n咁租機要交按金都好合理，本身佢地都有講明話還咗機check過冇問題就會即刻退番錢。<br />\n到今日上去還完機，個同事都check過哂都冇問題，但就話因為老細hold住咗個account唔喺度，所以要遲啲先退得番按金。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁我以為只係講緊等幾個鐘，都信佢哋打開門口做生意唔會幾千蚊都呃，所以就走咗。<br />\n但去到今晚都收唔到，喺whatsapp再追，佢哋嘅態度好似變咗我欠佢哋咁，話今日內會處理，但又冇咗件事...<br />\n見到佢地之後online都冇再覆我message，想問有冇巴打都畀佢哋拖過按金？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n圖：<br />\n依個conversation完咗就再冇覆過我，明明有online過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7C3tZ4f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7C3tZ4f.png&h=005c4431&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而本身租機嗰陣係有講明還機後會即時會退番按金。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7OJUVCJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7OJUVCJ.jpg&h=39ad272d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4ec4862bda5dc1a1178ecb4e8f79ae70cea5d4dd","tid":2294080,"uid":295230,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T17:38:19.000Z","msg":"租過幾次都買過野，老2個老闆好人黎，應該無事既，最近佢地請左人幫手處理野，可能覆你那個係員工所以態度9少少"},{"pid":"5c750a5f3bcce7e9e399ba014f8f1f9eb653cee3","tid":2294080,"uid":244832,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T18:40:24.000Z","msg":"借過幾次都冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stretching.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bc7b916cc0171f55d1bffe0ac69c5f312c06b44","tid":2294080,"uid":14541,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T19:04:57.000Z","msg":"呢間係正常公司嚟嘅<br />\n但係咁樣的確係有問題